---
import BaseLayout from '../components/BaseLayout.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home" description="AI governance and regulatory readiness for technology companies. Build responsible AI practices and prepare for regulatory requirements.">
  <HeroSection
    headline="AI Governance Readiness for Technology Companies"
    subheadline="Build responsible AI practices. Prepare for regulatory requirements. Demonstrate trustworthy AI."
    ctaText="Get Started"
    ctaHref="/about"
  />

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>Why AI Governance Matters</h2>
    <p>AI systems are increasingly subject to regulatory scrutiny, enterprise procurement requirements, and public expectations for responsible development. Without a governance framework, organizations face regulatory risk, lost deals, and reputational exposure.</p>
    <div class="value-grid">
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Build Responsible AI</h3>
        <p>AI governance frameworks help organizations develop and deploy AI systems responsibly, with systematic approaches to fairness, transparency, and accountability.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Prepare for AI Regulation</h3>
        <p>The EU AI Act, NIST AI RMF, and emerging state laws are creating enforceable AI requirements. Organizations that prepare now avoid costly retrofitting later.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Win Enterprise AI Deals</h3>
        <p>Enterprise buyers increasingly require AI governance documentation before procurement. Demonstrating responsible AI practices accelerates trust and closes deals.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <h3>Manage AI Risk</h3>
        <p>Systematic AI risk management reduces bias, safety, and reliability failures that can cause financial loss, regulatory action, and reputational damage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section">
    <h2>How We Help</h2>
    <p>Four service packages designed to meet you where you are in your AI governance journey.</p>
    <div class="service-overview-grid">
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Readiness Sprint</h3>
        <p>Scope, assess, and plan in 2&#8211;4 weeks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Governance Framework</h3>
        <p>Build policies, processes, and oversight</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Risk Assessment</h3>
        <p>Categorize and mitigate AI system risks</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/services" class="card service-overview-card">
        <h3>Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
        <p>Maintain governance as systems evolve</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content section cta-section">
    <h2>Ready to Get Started?</h2>
    <p>Whether you're building your first AI governance framework or need help preparing for the EU AI Act, we can help you demonstrate responsible AI with confidence.</p>
    <a href="/about" class="cta-button">Let's Talk</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-item h3 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .service-overview-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card {
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .service-overview-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-heading);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .service-overview-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem var(--spacing-page);
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .cta-section p {
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .service-overview-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
